<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= titolo %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <a href="/chi-siamo">Chi Siamo</a>
        <a href="/progetto">Progetto</a>
        <a href="/storia">Storia</a>
        <a href="/dashboard" style="background: #4a90d9;">Dashboard Petoi</a>
    </nav>
    <main>
        <h1><%= titolo %></h1>
        <p class="subtitle"><%= sottotitolo %></p>
        <h2 style="color: #1a3a5c; text-align: center; margin: 40px 0 20px; font-weight: normal;">Il Nostro Team</h2>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <div class="team-member" data-class="CW" style="position: relative; background: #0d1b2a; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; font-size: 1.1em; letter-spacing: 1px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;">
                Sofia
                <span class="team-class" style="position: absolute; bottom: -35px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: #4a90d9; color: white; padding: 5px 15px; font-size: 0.75em; border-radius: 5px; white-space: nowrap; opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.3s;">Cyberworld (CW)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member" data-class="AI" style="position: relative; background: #0d1b2a; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; font-size: 1.1em; letter-spacing: 1px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;">
                Massimo
                <span class="team-class" style="position: absolute; bottom: -35px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: #e74c3c; color: white; padding: 5px 15px; font-size: 0.75em; border-radius: 5px; white-space: nowrap; opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.3s;">Intelligenza Artificiale (AI)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member" data-class="AI" style="position: relative; background: #0d1b2a; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; font-size: 1.1em; letter-spacing: 1px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;">
                Aurora
                <span class="team-class" style="position: absolute; bottom: -35px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: #e74c3c; color: white; padding: 5px 15px; font-size: 0.75em; border-radius: 5px; white-space: nowrap; opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.3s;">Intelligenza Artificiale (AI)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member" data-class="IOT" style="position: relative; background: #0d1b2a; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; font-size: 1.1em; letter-spacing: 1px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;">
                Thomas
                <span class="team-class" style="position: absolute; bottom: -35px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: #27ae60; color: white; padding: 5px 15px; font-size: 0.75em; border-radius: 5px; white-space: nowrap; opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.3s;">Internet of Things (IOT)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member" data-class="CW" style="position: relative; background: #0d1b2a; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; font-size: 1.1em; letter-spacing: 1px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;">
                Ambra
                <span class="team-class" style="position: absolute; bottom: -35px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: #4a90d9; color: white; padding: 5px 15px; font-size: 0.75em; border-radius: 5px; white-space: nowrap; opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.3s;">Cyberworld (CW)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member" data-class="IOT" style="position: relative; background: #0d1b2a; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; font-size: 1.1em; letter-spacing: 1px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;">
                Giacomo
                <span class="team-class" style="position: absolute; bottom: -35px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: #27ae60; color: white; padding: 5px 15px; font-size: 0.75em; border-radius: 5px; white-space: nowrap; opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.3s;">Internet of Things (IOT)</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Siamo studenti che hanno partecipato a una summer school per la passione dell'informatica e del nuovo mondo che sta arrivando. Durante questo percorso formativo abbiamo avuto l'opportunità di approfondire le tecnologie più innovative e di confrontarci con esperti del settore.</p>
            <p>In questi giorni abbiamo lavorato divisi in tre classi, ciascuna dedicata a un ambito specifico: Cyberworld, Intelligenza Artificiale e Internet of Things. Ogni gruppo ha sviluppato competenze specialistiche, imparando a padroneggiare strumenti e metodologie all'avanguardia.</p>
            <p>Unendo le nostre conoscenze e competenze acquisite, abbiamo realizzato un progetto importante che rappresenta la sintesi del nostro lavoro e della nostra collaborazione. Il progetto è il frutto dell'integrazione tra le diverse discipline che abbiamo esplorato insieme.</p>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>Colombo App 2026</p>
    </footer>
    <script src="/js/rocks.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/ships.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/remote-control.js"></script>
    <script>
        document.querySelectorAll('.team-member').forEach(member => {
            member.addEventListener('mouseenter', function() {
                this.querySelector('.team-class').style.opacity = '1';
                this.style.transform = 'translateY(-5px)';
                this.style.boxShadow = '0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3)';
            });
            
            member.addEventListener('mouseleave', function() {
                this.querySelector('.team-class').style.opacity = '0';
                this.style.transform = 'translateY(0)';
                this.style.boxShadow = 'none';
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
